OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,6,Fday with patchy cloud. A few showers
OL,7,Fmay develop from late morning, these
OL,8,Fmostly light and clearing away through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers will clear this
OL,12,Fevening. The rest of the night will be
OL,13,Fdry with clear spells, allowing some
OL,14,Fpatches of mist and fog to develop.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FAny early morning mist or fog
OL,17,Fpatches quickly clearing. Then dry and
OL,18,Fsettled for the rest of the day with a
OL,19,Fgood deal of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
