OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled throughout this period
OL,7,Fwith a good deal of sunshine. Light
OL,8,Fwinds at first but becoming breezier
OL,9,Fby Thursday on eastern coasts.
